{"_id":"02e1a7198873937f","name":"Viper-Series_Probe_Droid","type":"droid","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","system":{"degree":"4th-Degree","initiative":6,"senses":"Perception","perception":9,"reflexDefense":16,"flatFooted":15,"fortitudeDefense":16,"willDefense":13,"HP":34,"damageThreshold":21,"speed":6,"baseAttackBonus":null,"grapple":null,"attacks":{"melee":[{"name":"Unarmed","bonus":4,"damage":"1d6+4"}],"ranged":[{"name":"Blaster","bonus":1,"damage":"3d6"}]},"baseStats":{"abilities":{"strength":18,"dexterity":12,"intelligence":12,"wisdom":15,"charisma":11,"constitution":0}},"skills":{"Endurance":5,"Initiative":6,"Perception":9,"Stealth":1,"Survival":7},"type":"droid","description":"","costNumeric":20250,"category":"droid","cost":20250,"droidDegreeKey":"4th-degree","droidRole":"recon","droidRoleLabel":"Recon","droidSystemText":"Hovering Locomotion, Basic Processor , 2 Hand Appendages, 2 Claw Appendages, 2 Tool Mounts, Darkvision , Improved Sensor Package , Locked Access , Internal Comlink , Self-Destruct System (4d6)","droidSystems":{"processor":{"id":"basic-processor","name":"Basic Processor","source":"published"},"locomotion":[{"id":"hovering-locomotion","name":"Hovering Locomotion","source":"published"}],"appendages":[{"id":"2-hand-appendages","name":"2 Hand Appendages","source":"published"},{"id":"2-claw-appendages","name":"2 Claw Appendages","source":"published"},{"id":"2-tool-mounts","name":"2 Tool Mounts","source":"published"}],"sensors":[{"id":"darkvision","name":"Darkvision","source":"published"},{"id":"improved-sensor-package","name":"Improved Sensor Package","source":"published"}],"integratedSystems":[{"id":"locked-access","name":"Locked Access","source":"published"},{"id":"internal-comlink","name":"Internal Comlink","source":"published"}],"accessories":[{"id":"self-destruct-system-4d6","name":"Self-Destruct System (4d6)","source":"published"}],"weapons":[{"id":"blaster","name":"Blaster","mode":"ranged","damage":"3d6","attackBonus":1,"source":"published-attack"}],"sourceText":"Hovering Locomotion, Basic Processor , 2 Hand Appendages, 2 Claw Appendages, 2 Tool Mounts, Darkvision , Improved Sensor Package , Locked Access , Internal Comlink , Self-Destruct System (4d6)","sourcePossessions":"Blaster (as Blaster Pistol ), Video Recording Unit , Sensor Unit, Durasteel Shell ( Droid Armor ; +4 Reflex ) Availability: Restricted ; Cost: 20,250 credits Viper-Series Probe Droid Protocol Format [ ] Reference Book: Star Wars Saga Edition Scavenger's Guide to Droids See also: Protocol Format Medium 4th-Degree Droid Hit Points: 34 Damage Threshold : 21 System Actions [ ] Move (1 Swift Action , 2/Turn) [ ] The Viper-Series Probe Droid moves 6 squares ( Hovering ). Pacify Hostile (1 Swift Action , 1/Turn) [ ] The Viper-Series Probe Droid makes a ranged attack at +1. If successful, the attack deals 3d6 points of damage. Patrol Duty (1 Swift Action , 1/Turn) [ ] The Viper-Series Probe Droid makes a Perception check against a target's Stealth check. If the check is successful, the Droid detects the target. Scan (2 Swift Actions , 1/Turn) [ ] The Viper-Series Probe Droid selects an adjacent square and makes a DC 15 Perception check. If the Droid's check is successful, the Droid discovers any clues, secret doors, hidden compartments, irregularities, traps, or anything else out of the ordinary. The Droid can communicate its discoveries as a Free Action . Self-Destruct (1 Free Action ) [ ] The Viper-Series Probe Droid activates its self-destruct mechanism. The Droid makes a 2-Square Burst attack at +5. If successful, the attack deals 4d6 points of damage. The Droid is immediately destroyed. Base Stats [ ]"},"cl":1},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"swse":{"speedText":"6 Squares ( Hovering )","droidSystemText":"Hovering Locomotion, Basic Processor , 2 Hand Appendages, 2 Claw Appendages, 2 Tool Mounts, Darkvision , Improved Sensor Package , Locked Access , Internal Comlink , Self-Destruct System (4d6)"}}}
