{"_id":"0ecb09a9d105d4ed","name":"Wanderer_Scout_Surveyor_Droid","type":"droid","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","system":{"degree":"5th-Degree","initiative":null,"senses":"Perception","perception":6,"reflexDefense":16,"flatFooted":16,"fortitudeDefense":14,"willDefense":12,"HP":26,"damageThreshold":14,"speed":6,"baseAttackBonus":null,"grapple":null,"attacks":{"melee":[{"name":"Unarmed","bonus":2,"damage":"1d4"}],"ranged":[{"name":"Stun Blaster","bonus":3,"damage":"3d6 ( Stun"},{"name":"Stun Blaster","bonus":3,"damage":"3d6 ( Stun"}]},"baseStats":{"abilities":{"strength":14,"dexterity":16,"intelligence":8,"wisdom":13,"charisma":3,"constitution":0}},"skills":{"Climb":7,"Jump":7,"Perception":6,"Survival":6,"Treat Injury":6},"type":"droid","description":"","costNumeric":9400,"category":"droid","cost":9400,"droidDegreeKey":"5th-degree","droidRole":"survey","droidRoleLabel":"Survey","droidSystemText":"Walking Locomotion, Extra Legs , Basic Processor , 1 Claw Appendage, 4 Tool Mounts","droidSystems":{"processor":{"id":"basic-processor","name":"Basic Processor","source":"published"},"locomotion":[{"id":"walking-locomotion","name":"Walking Locomotion","source":"published"}],"appendages":[{"id":"1-claw-appendage","name":"1 Claw Appendage","source":"published"},{"id":"4-tool-mounts","name":"4 Tool Mounts","source":"published"}],"sensors":[],"integratedSystems":[],"accessories":[{"id":"extra-legs","name":"Extra Legs","source":"published"}],"weapons":[{"id":"stun-blaster","name":"Stun Blaster","mode":"ranged","damage":"3d6 ( Stun","attackBonus":3,"source":"published-attack"},{"id":"stun-blaster","name":"Stun Blaster","mode":"ranged","damage":"3d6 ( Stun","attackBonus":3,"source":"published-attack"}],"sourceText":"Walking Locomotion, Extra Legs , Basic Processor , 1 Claw Appendage, 4 Tool Mounts","sourcePossessions":"Stun Blaster (As Blaster Pistol set to Stun ), Sensor Pack , Surgery Kit Availability: Licensed ; Cost: 9,400 credits Abilities [ ] 360-Degree Vision: Although it is not able to constantly see everything around it, the Scout Surveyor Droid can turn the photoreceptor mounted on top of the Droid in any direction, allowing the Droid to retain its Dexterity bonus to its Reflex Defense : regardless of being caught Flat-Footed or struck by a hidden attacker. The Droid also cannot be Flanked . Wanderer Scout Surveyor Droid Protocol Format [ ] See also: Protocol Format Medium 5th-Degree Droid Hit Points: 26 Damage Threshold : 14 System Actions [ ] Move (1 Swift Action , 2/Turn) [ ] The Wanderer Scout Surveyor Droid moves 4 squares ( Walking ). Accelerated Climbing (1 Swift Action , 2/Turn) [ ] With a successful Climb check (+7), the Wanderer Scout Surveyor Droid can climb at half its full speed. Notice Targets ( Reaction ) [ ] As a Reaction , with a successful Perception check, the Wanderer Scout Surveyor Droid can notice targets that come within its line of sight. Actively searching for hidden enemies is a Standard Action . Sensor Sweep (2 Swift Actions , 1/Turn) [ ] The Wanderer Scout Surveyor Droid can detect lifeforms within a 24-square range with a successful Perception check. Stun Blast (2 Swift Actions , 1/Turn) [ ] The Wanderer Scout Surveyor Droid makes a ranged attack at +3. If successful, the attack deals 3d6 points of Stun Damage . Track (2 Swift Actions , 1/Turn) [ ] The Wanderer Scout Surveyor Droid can Track with a successful Survival check. Base Stats [ ]"},"cl":1},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"swse":{"speedText":"6 Squares ( Walking )","droidSystemText":"Walking Locomotion, Extra Legs , Basic Processor , 1 Claw Appendage, 4 Tool Mounts"}}}
