{"_id":"13ad17827ba38b69","name":"DSH-3_Probe_Droid","type":"droid","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","system":{"degree":"4th-Degree","initiative":null,"senses":"Perception","perception":15,"reflexDefense":15,"flatFooted":11,"fortitudeDefense":8,"willDefense":12,"HP":8,"damageThreshold":8,"speed":6,"baseAttackBonus":null,"grapple":null,"attacks":{"melee":[],"ranged":[]},"baseStats":{"abilities":{"strength":6,"dexterity":18,"intelligence":12,"wisdom":14,"charisma":9,"constitution":0}},"skills":{"Perception":15,"Stealth":20,"Survival":13},"type":"droid","description":"","costNumeric":13000,"category":"droid","cost":13000,"droidDegreeKey":"4th-degree","droidRole":"recon","droidRoleLabel":"Recon","droidSystemText":"Hovering Locomotion, Heuristic Processor , Darkvision , Improved Sensor Package , Internal Comlink , Locked Access , Secondary Battery","droidSystems":{"processor":{"id":"heuristic-processor","name":"Heuristic Processor","source":"published"},"locomotion":[{"id":"hovering-locomotion","name":"Hovering Locomotion","source":"published"}],"appendages":[],"sensors":[{"id":"darkvision","name":"Darkvision","source":"published"},{"id":"improved-sensor-package","name":"Improved Sensor Package","source":"published"}],"integratedSystems":[{"id":"internal-comlink","name":"Internal Comlink","source":"published"},{"id":"locked-access","name":"Locked Access","source":"published"},{"id":"secondary-battery","name":"Secondary Battery","source":"published"}],"accessories":[],"weapons":[],"sourceText":"Hovering Locomotion, Heuristic Processor , Darkvision , Improved Sensor Package , Internal Comlink , Locked Access , Secondary Battery","sourcePossessions":"Audio Recorder , Video Recorder Availability: Licensed ; Cost: 13,000 credits Abilities [ ] Easily Hidden: The DSH-3 Probe Droid can hide more easily than other Droids of similar size and function. It can Take 10 on a Stealth check even when distracted or threatened. DSH-3 Probe Droid Protocol Format [ ] See also: Protocol Format Small 4th-Degree Droid Hit Points: 8 Damage Threshold : 8 System Actions [ ] Move (1 Swift Action , 2/Turn) [ ] The DSH-3 Probe Droid moves 6 squares ( Hovering ). Avoid Surprise ( Free Action ) [ ] The DSH-3 Probe Droid makes a Perception check at the start of a battle. If the check is successful, the Droid's master avoids Surprise . Create a Diversion to Hide (2 Swift Actions , 1/Turn) [ ] The DSH-3 Probe Droid can make a Deception check to Create a Diversion to Hide and give the DSH-3 Probe Droid time to hide. Easily Hidden (2 Swift Actions , 1/Turn) [ ] The DSH-3 Probe Droid can Take 10 on its Stealth check to Sneak even when distracted or threatened. Sneak (1 Swift Action , 1/Turn) [ ] The DSH-3 Probe Droid can slip past an opponent without being noticed by making a successful Stealth check opposed by the opponent's Perception check. Track (2 Swift Actions , 1/Turn) [ ] The DSH-3 Probe Droid can Track with a successful Survival check. Base Stats [ ]"},"cl":1},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"swse":{"speedText":"6 Squares ( Hovering )","droidSystemText":"Hovering Locomotion, Heuristic Processor , Darkvision , Improved Sensor Package , Internal Comlink , Locked Access , Secondary Battery"}}}
