{"_id":"262e21c29f6f8ea4","name":"KM1_Mining_Droid","type":"droid","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","system":{"degree":"5th-Degree","initiative":null,"senses":"Perception","perception":2,"reflexDefense":17,"flatFooted":17,"fortitudeDefense":17,"willDefense":9,"HP":31,"damageThreshold":22,"speed":6,"baseAttackBonus":null,"grapple":null,"attacks":{"melee":[{"name":"Unarmed","bonus":11,"damage":"1d4+7"},{"name":"Unarmed","bonus":10,"damage":"1d4+14"}],"ranged":[{"name":"Laser Cutter","bonus":4,"damage":"3d8"},{"name":"Laser Cutter","bonus":4,"damage":"3d8"}]},"baseStats":{"abilities":{"strength":24,"dexterity":10,"intelligence":10,"wisdom":8,"charisma":8,"constitution":0}},"skills":{"Endurance":8,"Perception":2},"type":"droid","description":"","costNumeric":21880,"category":"droid","cost":21880,"droidDegreeKey":"5th-degree","droidRole":"mining","droidRoleLabel":"Mining","droidSystemText":"Walking Locomotion, Extra Legs , Basic Processor , 2 Tool Mounts, Darkvision , Mining Shield Generator","droidSystems":{"processor":{"id":"basic-processor","name":"Basic Processor","source":"published"},"locomotion":[{"id":"walking-locomotion","name":"Walking Locomotion","source":"published"}],"appendages":[{"id":"2-tool-mounts","name":"2 Tool Mounts","source":"published"}],"sensors":[{"id":"darkvision","name":"Darkvision","source":"published"}],"integratedSystems":[{"id":"mining-shield-generator","name":"Mining Shield Generator","source":"published"}],"accessories":[{"id":"extra-legs","name":"Extra Legs","source":"published"}],"weapons":[{"id":"laser-cutter","name":"Laser Cutter","mode":"ranged","damage":"3d8","attackBonus":4,"source":"published-attack"},{"id":"laser-cutter","name":"Laser Cutter","mode":"ranged","damage":"3d8","attackBonus":4,"source":"published-attack"}],"sourceText":"Walking Locomotion, Extra Legs , Basic Processor , 2 Tool Mounts, Darkvision , Mining Shield Generator","sourcePossessions":"Laser Cutter (2; as Heavy Blaster Pistol with a maximum range of 12 squares), Duranium Plating ( Droid Armor ; +8 Reflex ) Availability: Licensed ; Cost: 21,880 credits Abilities [ ] Adaptable Programming: The KM1 Mining Droid is built for easy adaptation to tasks. The DC of Use Computer checks to Reprogram the Droid is reduced by 5. Mining Shield Generator: This device operates as a normal Shield Generator (SR 10) and enables the KM1 Mining Droid to reroll Endurance checks and take the better result to resist environmental damage and effects. KM1 Mining Droid Protocol Format [ ] See also: Protocol Format Large 5th-Degree Droid Hit Points: 31 Damage Threshold : 22 (SR 10) System Actions [ ] Move (1 Swift Action , 2/Turn) [ ] The KM1 Mining Droid moves 6 squares ( Walking ). Adaptable Programming ( Free Action ) [ ] When Reprogramming a KM1 Mining Droid, reduce the DC of the Use Computer check by 5. Improvised Fire (1 Swift Action , 1/Turn) [ ] The KM1 Mining Droid makes a ranged attack at +4 (with a maximum range of 12 squares). If successful, the attack deals 3d8 points of damage. Slammer (1 Swift Action , 1/Turn) [ ] The KM1 Mining Droid makes a melee attack at +10. If successful, the attack deals 1d4+14 points of damage. If the damage exceeds the target's Damage Threshold , the target also gains a Persistent Condition . Stability ( Free Action ) [ ] The KM1 Mining Droid gains a +5 bonus to avoid being knocked Prone . Base Stats [ ]"},"cl":2},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"swse":{"speedText":"6 Squares ( Walking )","droidSystemText":"Walking Locomotion, Extra Legs , Basic Processor , 2 Tool Mounts, Darkvision , Mining Shield Generator"}}}
