{"_id":"2cdc3e761128b6e0","name":"TT-8L_Gatekeeper_Droid","type":"droid","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","system":{"degree":"3rd-Degree","initiative":null,"senses":"Perception","perception":14,"reflexDefense":6,"flatFooted":6,"fortitudeDefense":10,"willDefense":12,"HP":13,"damageThreshold":15,"speed":null,"baseAttackBonus":null,"grapple":null,"attacks":{"melee":[{"name":"Unarmed","bonus":0,"damage":"1d4"}],"ranged":[]},"baseStats":{"abilities":{"strength":10,"dexterity":4,"intelligence":13,"wisdom":14,"charisma":16,"constitution":0}},"skills":{"Perception":14,"Persuasion":13},"type":"droid","description":"","costNumeric":5970,"category":"droid","cost":5970,"droidDegreeKey":"3rd-degree","droidRole":"information","droidRoleLabel":"Information","droidSystemText":"Remote Receiver , 1 Tool Mount ( Telescopic Appendage ), Darkvision , Improved Sensor Package , Vocabulator Availability: Licensed ; Cost: 5,970 credits Abilities [ ] Stubborn: The TT-8L Gatekeeper Droid's personality makes it a stubborn negotiator. When Persuasion checks are made against the Droid, it adds its Charisma bonus to its Will Defense . TT-8L Gatekeeper Droid Protocol Format [ ] See also: Protocol Format Large 3rd-Degree Droid Hit Points: 13 Damage Threshold : 15 System Actions [ ] Eavesdrop (1 Swift Action , 1/Turn) [ ] The TT-8L Gatekeeper Droid can make a Perception check to listen in on conversations and learn information. Intimidate (2 Swift Actions , 1/Turn) [ ] With a successful Persuasion check, the TT-8L Gatekeeper Droid can force a single creature to back down from a confrontation, reveal secret information, or flee. Sense Deception ( Reaction ) [ ] The TT-8L Gatekeeper Droid can make a Perception check to see through deceptive appearances made using the Deception skill. Stubborn ( Free Action ) [ ] When Persuasion checks are made against its master, the TT- 8L Gatekeeper Droid adds its Charisma bonus to its master's Will Defense . Base Stats [ ] Skills : Knowledge (Bureaucracy) +6, Perception +14, Persuasion +13 Vital Systems: 1 Tool Mount ( Telescopic Appendage ), Vocabulator","droidSystems":{"processor":{"id":"remote-receiver","name":"Remote Receiver","source":"published"},"locomotion":[],"appendages":[{"id":"1-tool-mount-telescopic-appendage","name":"1 Tool Mount ( Telescopic Appendage )","source":"published"},{"id":"persuasion-13-vital-systems-1-tool-mount-telescopic-appendage","name":"Persuasion +13 Vital Systems: 1 Tool Mount ( Telescopic Appendage )","source":"published"}],"sensors":[{"id":"darkvision","name":"Darkvision","source":"published"},{"id":"improved-sensor-package","name":"Improved Sensor Package","source":"published"}],"integratedSystems":[{"id":"vocabulator-availability-licensed-cost-5","name":"Vocabulator Availability: Licensed ; Cost: 5","source":"published"},{"id":"vocabulator","name":"Vocabulator","source":"published"}],"accessories":[{"id":"970-credits-abilities-stubborn-the-tt-8l-gatekeeper-droids-personality-makes-it-a-stubborn-negotiator-when-persuasion-checks-are-made-against-the-droid","name":"970 credits Abilities [ ] Stubborn: The TT-8L Gatekeeper Droid's personality makes it a stubborn negotiator. When Persuasion checks are made against the Droid","source":"published"},{"id":"it-adds-its-charisma-bonus-to-its-will-defense-tt-8l-gatekeeper-droid-protocol-format-see-also-protocol-format-large-3rd-degree-droid-hit-points-13-damage-threshold-15-system-actions-eavesdrop-1-swift-action-1-turn-the-tt-8l-gatekeeper-droid-can-make-a-perception-check-to-listen-in-on-conversations-and-learn-information-intimidate-2-swift-actions-1-turn-with-a-successful-persuasion-check","name":"it adds its Charisma bonus to its Will Defense . TT-8L Gatekeeper Droid Protocol Format [ ] See also: Protocol Format Large 3rd-Degree Droid Hit Points: 13 Damage Threshold : 15 System Actions [ ] Eavesdrop (1 Swift Action, 1/Turn) [ ] The TT-8L Gatekeeper Droid can make a Perception check to listen in on conversations and learn information. Intimidate