{"_id":"2ea9e1f3f6800831","name":"RWW-Series_Protocol_Droid","type":"droid","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","system":{"degree":"3rd-Degree","initiative":null,"senses":"Perception","perception":0,"reflexDefense":9,"flatFooted":9,"fortitudeDefense":8,"willDefense":10,"HP":3,"damageThreshold":8,"speed":6,"baseAttackBonus":null,"grapple":null,"attacks":{"melee":[{"name":"Unarmed","bonus":-2,"damage":"1d3-2"}],"ranged":[]},"baseStats":{"abilities":{"strength":7,"dexterity":8,"intelligence":12,"wisdom":10,"charisma":14,"constitution":0}},"skills":{"Deception":7,"Perception":0,"Persuasion":12},"type":"droid","description":"","costNumeric":5505,"category":"droid","cost":5505,"droidDegreeKey":"3rd-degree","droidRole":"protocol","droidRoleLabel":"Protocol","droidSystemText":"Walking Locomotion, Basic Processor , 2 Hand Appendages, Translator Unit (DC 10), Vocabulator Availability: Licensed ; Cost: 5,505 credits Abilities [ ] Mimic: As a Swift Action , the RWW-Series Protocol Droid can reroll a Deception check when attempting to imitate the speech patterns and gestures of a selected character but must take the result of the second roll, even if it is worse. RWW-Series Protocol Droid Protocol Format [ ] See also: Protocol Format Medium 3rd-Degree Droid Hit Points: 3 Damage Threshold : 8 System Actions [ ] Move (1 Swift Action , 2/Turn) [ ] The RWW-Series Protocol Droid moves 6 squares ( Walking ). Databank (1 Swift Action ) [ ] The RWW-Series Protocol Droid can attempt a Knowledge check involving Bureaucracy, Galactic Lore, or Social Sciences. If the check is successful, the Droid communicates the information to its master. Mimic (1 Swift Action ) [ ] The RWW-Series Protocol Droid can imitate an individual of its master's choosing, gaining a +2 bonus to a Deception check made to produce a Deceptive Appearance . Translator (1 Free Action ) [ ] With a DC 10 Intelligence check, the RWW-Series Protocol Droid translates to or from any language it knows. Base Stats [ ] Skills : Deception +7, Knowledge (Bureaucracy) +6, Knowledge (Galactic Lore) +11, Persuasion +12 Vital Systems: 2 Hand Appendages, Translator Unit (DC 10), Vocabulator","droidSystems":{"processor":{"id":"basic-processor","name":"Basic Processor","source":"published"},"locomotion":[{"id":"walking-locomotion","name":"Walking Locomotion","source":"published"},{"id":"even-if-it-is-worse-rww-series-protocol-droid-protocol-format-see-also-protocol-format-medium-3rd-degree-droid-hit-points-3-damage-threshold-8-system-actions-move-1-swift-action-2-turn-the-rww-series-protocol-droid-moves-6-squares-walking-databank-1-swift-action-the-rww-series-protocol-droid-can-attempt-a-knowledge-check-involving-bureaucracy","name":"even if it is worse. RWW-Series Protocol Droid Protocol Format [ ] See also: Protocol Format Medium 3rd-Degree Droid Hit Points: 3 Damage Threshold : 8 System Actions [ ] Move (1 Swift Action, 2/Turn) [ ] The RWW-Series Protocol Droid moves 6 squares ( Walking ). Databank (1 Swift Action ) [ ] The RWW-Series Protocol Droid can attempt a Knowledge check involving Bureaucracy","source":"published"}],"appendages":[{"id":"2-hand-appendages","name":"2 Hand Appendages","source":"published"},{"id":"persuasion-12-vital-systems-2-hand-appendages","name":"Persuasion +12 Vital Systems: 2 Hand Appendages","source":"published"}],"sensors":[],"integratedSystems":[{"id":"translator-unit-dc-10","name":"Translator Unit (DC 10)","source":"published"},{"id":"vocabulator-availability-licensed-cost-5","name":"Vocabulator Availability: Licensed ; Cost: 5","source":"published"},{"id":"gaining-a-2-bonus-to-a-deception-check-made-to-produce-a-deceptive-appearance-translator-1-free-action-with-a-dc-10-intelligence-check","name":"gaining a +2 bonus to a Deception check made to produce a Deceptive Appearance . Translator (1 Free Action ) [ ] With a DC 10 Intelligence check","source":"published"},{"id":"translator-unit-dc-10","name":"Translator Unit (DC 10)","source":"published"},{"id":"vocabulator",