even if it is worse. RWW-Series Protocol Droid Protocol Format [ ] See also: Protocol Format Medium 3rd-Degree Droid Hit Points: 3 Damage Threshold : 8 System Actions [ ] Move (1 Swift Action , 2/Turn) [ ] The RWW-Series Protocol Droid moves 6 squares ( Walking ). Databank (1 Swift Action ) [ ] The RWW-Series Protocol Droid can attempt a Knowledge check involving Bureaucracy, Galactic Lore, or Social Sciences. If the check is successful, the Droid communicates the information to its master. Mimic (1 Swift Action ) [ ] The RWW-Series Protocol Droid can imitate an individual of its master's choosing, gaining a +2 bonus to a Deception check made to produce a Deceptive Appearance . Translator (1 Free Action ) [ ] With a DC 10 Intelligence check, the RWW-Series Protocol Droid translates to or from any language it knows. Base Stats [ ] Skills : Deception +7, Knowledge (Bureaucracy) +6, Knowledge (Galactic Lore) +11, Persuasion +12 Vital Systems: 2 Hand Appendages, Translator Unit (DC 10), Vocabulator"},"cl":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"swse":{"speedText":"6 Squares ( Walking )","droidSystemText":"Walking Locomotion, Basic Processor , 2 Hand Appendages, Translator Unit (DC 10), Vocabulator Availability: Licensed ; Cost: 5,505 credits Abilities [ ] Mimic: As a Swift Action , the RWW-Series Protocol Droid can reroll a Deception check when attempting to imitate the speech patterns and gestures of a selected character but must take the result of the second roll, even if it is worse. RWW-Series Protocol Droid Protocol Format [ ] See also: Protocol Format Medium 3rd-Degree Droid Hit Points: 3 Damage Threshold : 8 System Actions [ ] Move (1 Swift Action , 2/Turn) [ ] The RWW-Series Protocol Droid moves 6 squares ( Walking ). Databank (1 Swift Action ) [ ] The RWW-Series Protocol Droid can attempt a Knowledge check involving Bureaucracy, Galactic Lore, or Social Sciences. If the check is successful, the Droid communicates the information to its master. Mimic (1 Swift Action ) [ ] The RWW-Series Protocol Droid can imitate an individual of its master's choosing, gaining a +2 bonus to a Deception check made to produce a Deceptive Appearance . Translator (1 Free Action ) [ ] With a DC 10 Intelligence check, the RWW-Series Protocol Droid translates to or from any language it knows. Base Stats [ ] Skills : Deception +7, Knowledge (Bureaucracy) +6, Knowledge (Galactic Lore) +11, Persuasion +12 Vital Systems: 2 Hand Appendages, Translator Unit (DC 10), Vocabulator"}}}
{"_id":"2fcf39ab1e0fec32","name":"HK-24_Assassin_Droid","type":"droid","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","system":{"degree":"4th-Degree","initiative":13,"senses":"Perception","perception":8,"reflexDefense":23,"flatFooted":20,"fortitudeDefense":19,"willDefense":16,"HP":43,"damageThreshold":19,"speed":6,"baseAttackBonus":null,"grapple":null,"attacks":{"melee":[{"name":"Unarmed","bonus":11,"damage":"1d3+4"}],"ranged":[]},"baseStats":{"abilities":{"strength":14,"dexterity":17,"intelligence":10,"wisdom":12,"charisma":13,"constitution":0}},"skills":{"Initiative":13,"Perception":8,"Persuasion":11},"type":"droid","description":"","costNumeric":30700,"category":"droid","cost":30700,"droidDegreeKey":"4th-degree","droidRole":"assassin","droidRoleLabel":"Assassin","droidSystemText":"Walking Locomotion, Heuristic Processor , 2 Hand Appendages, 2 Tool Appendages, Improved Sensor Package , Translator Unit (DC 5), Vocabulator","droidSystems":{"processor":{"id":"heuristic-processor","name":"Heuristic Processor","source":"published"},"locomotion":[{"id":"walking-locomotion","name":"Walking Locomotion","source":"published"}],"appendages":[{"id":"2-hand-appendages","name":"2 Hand Appendages","source":"published"},{"id":"2-tool-appendages","name":"2 Tool Appendages","source":"published"}],"sensors":[{"id":"improved-sensor-package","name":"Improved Sensor Package","source":"published"}],"integratedSystems":[{"id":"translator-unit-dc-5","name":"Translator Unit (DC 5)","source":"published"},{"id":"vocabulator","name":"Vocabulator","source":"published"}],"accessories":[],"weapons":[],"sourceText":"Walking Locomotion, Heuristic Processor , 2 Hand Appendages, 2 Tool Appendages, Improved Sensor Package , Translator Unit (DC 5), Vocabulator","sourcePossessions":"Blaster Rifle , Durasteel Battle Armor ( Droid Armor ; +8 Reflex ) Availability: Illegal , Rare ; Cost: Not available for sale (Estimated value 30,700 credits) HK-24 Assassin Droid Protocol Format [ ] Reference Book: Star Wars Saga Edition Scavenger's Guide to Droids See also: Protocol Format Medium 4th-Degree Droid Hit Points: 43 Damage Threshold : 19 System Actions [ ] Move (1 Swift Action , 2/Turn) [ ] The HK-24 Assassin Droid moves 6 squares ( Walking ). Intimidating Presence (2 Swift Actions , 1/Turn) [ ] The HK-24 Assassin Droid assists a character's Persuasion check, providing a +2 bonus to the check. Rapid Shot (1 Swift Action , 1/Turn) [ ] The HK-24 Assassin Droid makes a ranged attack at +11. If successful, the attack deals 4d8+4 points of damage. Support Fire (1 Swift Action , 1/Turn) [ ] The HK-24 Assassin Droid makes a ranged attack at +13. If successful, the attack deals 3d8+4 points of damage. Tactical Assistance (1 Swift Action , 1/Turn) [ ] The HK-24 Assassin Droid assists a character's ranged attack, providing a +2 bonus to the roll. Translator (1 Free Action ) [ ] With a DC 5 Intelligence check, the HK-24 Assassin Droid translates to or from any language it knows. Base Stats [ ]"},"cl":7},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"swse":{"speedText":"6 Squares ( Walking )","droidSystemText":"Walking Locomotion, Heuristic Processor , 2 Hand Appendages, 2 Tool Appendages, Improved Sensor Package , Translator Unit (DC 5), Vocabulator"}}}
{"_id":"3032ff5a0e8c2ccc","name":"G2_Repair_Droid","type":"droid","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","system":{"degree":"2nd-Degree","initiative":null,"senses":"Perception","perception":7,"reflexDefense":12,"flatFooted":11,"fortitudeDefense":10,"willDefense":10,"HP":3,"damageThreshold":10,"speed":4,"baseAttackBonus":null,"grapple":null,"attacks":{"melee":[{"name":"Unarmed","bonus":0,"damage":"1d2"}],"ranged":[]},"baseStats":{"abilities":{"strength":10,"dexterity":13,"intelligence":15,"wisdom":11,"charisma":8,"constitution":0}},"skills":{"Mechanics":12,"Perception":7,"Use Computer":12},"type":"droid","description":"","costNumeric":5210,"category":"droid","cost":5210,"droidDegreeKey":"2nd-degree","droidRole":"repair","droidRoleLabel":"Repair","droidSystemText":"Walking Locomotion, Basic Processor , 2 Hand Appendages, Darkvision , Diagnostics Package , Improved Sensor Package , Vocabulator","droidSystems":{"processor":{"id":"basic-processor","name":"Basic Processor","source":"published"},"locomotion":[{"id":"walking-locomotion","name":"Walking Locomotion","source":"published"}],"appendages":[{"id":"2-hand-appendages","name":"2 Hand Appendages","source":"published"}],"sensors":[{"id":"darkvision","name":"Darkvision","source":"published"},{"id":"improved-sensor-package","name":"Improved Sensor Package","source":"published"}],"integratedSystems":[{"id":"vocabulator","name":"Vocabulator","source":"published"}],"accessories":[{"id":"diagnostics-package","name":"Diagnostics Package","source":"published"}],"weapons":[],"sourceText":"Walking Locomotion, Basic Processor , 2 Hand Appendages, Darkvision , Diagnostics Package , Improved Sensor Package , Vocabulator","sourcePossessions":"Tool Kit Availability: Licensed ; Cost: 5,210 credits Abilities [ ] Patch Job: The G2 Repair Droid can make temporary repairs to any disabled mechanical or electronic device as a Standard Action instead of a Full-Round Action . G2 Repair Droid Protocol Format [ ] See also: Protocol Format Small 2nd-Degree Droid Hit Points: 3 Damage Threshold : 10 System Actions [ ] Move (1 Swift Action , 2/Turn) [ ] The G2 Repair Droid moves 4 squares ( Walking ). Patch Job (1 Swift Action , 1/Turn) [ ] The G2 Repair Droid makes fast, temporary repairs to any disabled mechanical or electronic device. The number of Hit Points restored equals the result of the Droid's Mechanics check. Recharge Shields (2 Swift Actions , 1/Turn) [ ] The G2 Repair Droid makes a DC 20 Mechanics check. If the check is successful, the Vehicle regains 5 SR, up to its normal maximum. Regulate Power (2 Swift Actions , 1/Turn) [ ] The G2 Repair Droid makes a DC 20 Mechanics check. If the check is successful, the Vehicle moves +1 step on on Condition Track . Run Diagnostics (1 Swift Action , 1/Turn) [ ] The G2 Repair Droid aids a character's Mechanics check, providing a +2 bonus to the check. Base Stats [ ]"},"cl":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"swse":{"speedText":"4 Squares ( Walking )","droidSystemText":"Walking Locomotion, Basic Processor , 2 Hand Appendages, Darkvision , Diagnostics Package , Improved Sensor Package , Vocabulator"}}}
