ved Sensor Package , Translator Unit (DC 5), Vocabulator","sourcePossessions":"Blaster Rifle , Comlink (Short-Range), Durasteel Shell ( Droid Armor ; +4 Reflex )"},"cl":1},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"swse":{"speedText":"6 Squares ( Walking )","droidSystemText":"Walking Locomotion, Heuristic Processor , 2 Hand Appendages, 2 Tool Mounts, Improved Sensor Package , Translator Unit (DC 5), Vocabulator"}}}
{"_id":"3520596115f9254b","name":"R8-Series_Astromech_Droid","type":"droid","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","system":{"degree":"2nd-Degree","initiative":null,"senses":"Perception","perception":8,"reflexDefense":12,"flatFooted":11,"fortitudeDefense":9,"willDefense":10,"HP":5,"damageThreshold":9,"speed":6,"baseAttackBonus":null,"grapple":null,"attacks":{"melee":[{"name":"Electroshock Probe","bonus":0,"damage":"1d8-1 ( Ion"}],"ranged":[{"name":"Laser Welder","bonus":2,"damage":"3d6"},{"name":"Laser Welder","bonus":2,"damage":"3d6"}]},"baseStats":{"abilities":{"strength":9,"dexterity":13,"intelligence":14,"wisdom":10,"charisma":8,"constitution":0}},"skills":{"Mechanics":13,"Perception":8,"Pilot":12,"Use Computer":13},"type":"droid","description":"","costNumeric":7990,"category":"droid","cost":7990,"droidDegreeKey":"2nd-degree","droidRole":"astromech","droidRoleLabel":"Astromech","droidSystemText":"Wheeled Locomotion, Walking Locomotion ( Exclusive ), Magnetic Feet , Heuristic Processor , 1 Claw Appendage, 4 Tool Mounts, Diagnostics Package , Improved Sensor Package , Internal Comlink , Scomp Link , Sensor Booster , Sensor Pack","droidSystems":{"processor":{"id":"heuristic-processor","name":"Heuristic Processor","source":"published"},"locomotion":[{"id":"wheeled-locomotion","name":"Wheeled Locomotion","source":"published"},{"id":"walking-locomotion-exclusive","name":"Walking Locomotion ( Exclusive )","source":"published"}],"appendages":[{"id":"1-claw-appendage","name":"1 Claw Appendage","source":"published"},{"id":"4-tool-mounts","name":"4 Tool Mounts","source":"published"}],"sensors":[{"id":"improved-sensor-package","name":"Improved Sensor Package","source":"published"},{"id":"sensor-booster","name":"Sensor Booster","source":"published"},{"id":"sensor-pack","name":"Sensor Pack","source":"published"}],"integratedSystems":[{"id":"internal-comlink","name":"Internal Comlink","source":"published"}],"accessories":[{"id":"magnetic-feet","name":"Magnetic Feet","source":"published"},{"id":"diagnostics-package","name":"Diagnostics Package","source":"published"},{"id":"scomp-link","name":"Scomp Link","source":"published"}],"weapons":[{"id":"electroshock-probe","name":"Electroshock Probe","mode":"melee","damage":"1d8-1 ( Ion","attackBonus":0,"source":"published-attack"},{"id":"laser-welder","name":"Laser Welder","mode":"ranged","damage":"3d6","attackBonus":2,"source":"published-attack"},{"id":"laser-welder","name":"Laser Welder","mode":"ranged","damage":"3d6","attackBonus":2,"source":"published-attack"}],"sourceText":"Wheeled Locomotion, Walking Locomotion ( Exclusive ), Magnetic Feet , Heuristic Processor , 1 Claw Appendage, 4 Tool Mounts, Diagnostics Package , Improved Sensor Package , Internal Comlink , Scomp Link , Sensor Booster , Sensor Pack","sourcePossessions":"Electroshock Probe , Fire Extinguisher , Holoprojector , Holorecorder , Astrogation Buffer (Storage Device, 6 Memory Units), Circular Saw, Laser Welder Availability: Licensed ; Cost: 7,990 credits Abilities [ ] Navigation Charts: Stored in the memory banks of the R8-Series Astromech Droid is a database of star charts that cover most of the known galaxy. Coordinating this information with its cutting-edge Astrogation Buffer, the Droid can calculate a course through Hyperspace as if it had access to The HoloNet , and does not take a -5 penalty to its Use Computer check. In addition, when time is of the essence, the Droid can calculate a course as a Standard Action instead of a Full-Round Action . R8-Series Astromech Droid Protocol Format [ ] See also: Protocol Format Small 2nd-Degree Droid Hit Points: 5 Damage Threshold : 9 System Actions [ ] Move (1 Swift Action , 2/Turn) [ ] The R8-Series Astromech Droid moves 6 squares ( Wheeled ). If the Droid takes two Swift Actions to move in the same turn, it changes into Walking mode and can move 4 squares. Copilot (1 Swift Action , 1/Turn) [ ] The R8-Series Astromech Droid aids a character's Pilot check, providing a +2 bonus to the check. Issue Routine Command (1 Swift Action , 1/Turn) [ ] The R8-Series Astromech Droid issues a routine command to a computer that has a Friendly Attitude toward it. Navigation Charts (1 Swift Action , 1/Turn) [ ] Even if the R8-Series Astromech Droid does not have access to The HoloNet , it can perform Astrogation as if it had access. Recharge Shields (2 Swift Actions , 1/Turn) [ ] The R8-Series Astromech Droid makes a DC 20 Mechanics check. If the check is successful, the Vehicle regains 5 SR, up to its normal maximum. Regulate Power (2 Swift Actions , 1/Turn) [ ] The R8-Series Astromech Droid makes a DC 20 Mechanics check. If the check is successful, the Vehicle moves +1 step on on Condition Track . Base Stats [ ]"},"cl":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"swse":{"speedText":"6 Squares ( Wheeled ), 4 Squares ( Walking ( Exclusive )); Magnetic Feet","droidSystemText":"Wheeled Locomotion, Walking Locomotion ( Exclusive ), Magnetic Feet , Heuristic Processor , 1 Claw Appendage, 4 Tool Mounts, Diagnostics Package , Improved Sensor Package , Internal Comlink , Scomp Link , Sensor Booster , Sensor Pack"}}}
