mando Droid moves 6 squares ( Walking ). Avoid Surprise ( Free Action ) [ ] The V2-Series Commando Droid makes a Perception check at the start of a battle. If the check is successful, the Droid's master avoids Surprise . Patrol Duty (1 Swift Action , 1/Turn) [ ] The V2-Series Commando Droid makes a Perception check against a target's Stealth check. If the check is successful, the Battle Droid detects the target. Silent Action (1 Swift Action , 1/Turn) [ ] The V2-Series Commando Droid assists a character's Stealth check, providing a +2 bonus to the check. Support Fire (2 Swift Actions , 1/Turn) [ ] The V2-Series Commando Droid makes a ranged attack at +2. If successful, the attack deals 3d8 points of damage. Base Stats [ ]"},"cl":1},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"swse":{"speedText":"6 Squares ( Walking )","droidSystemText":"Walking Locomotion, Heuristic Processor , 2 Hand Appendages, Vocabulator"}}}
