{"_id":"4375445748385b1f","name":"S19_Astromech_Droid","type":"droid","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","system":{"degree":"2nd-Degree","initiative":null,"senses":"Perception","perception":8,"reflexDefense":11,"flatFooted":11,"fortitudeDefense":10,"willDefense":12,"HP":4,"damageThreshold":10,"speed":4,"baseAttackBonus":null,"grapple":null,"attacks":{"melee":[{"name":"Unarmed","bonus":1,"damage":"1d3"}],"ranged":[]},"baseStats":{"abilities":{"strength":11,"dexterity":10,"intelligence":16,"wisdom":14,"charisma":11,"constitution":0}},"skills":{"Mechanics":14,"Perception":8,"Use Computer":14},"type":"droid","description":"","costNumeric":8625,"category":"droid","cost":8625,"droidDegreeKey":"2nd-degree","droidRole":"astromech","droidRoleLabel":"Astromech","droidSystemText":"Tracked Locomotion, Heuristic Processor , 1 Claw Appendage, 6 Tool Mounts, Diagnostics Package , Internal Comlink , Scomp Link","droidSystems":{"processor":{"id":"heuristic-processor","name":"Heuristic Processor","source":"published"},"locomotion":[{"id":"tracked-locomotion","name":"Tracked Locomotion","source":"published"}],"appendages":[{"id":"1-claw-appendage","name":"1 Claw Appendage","source":"published"},{"id":"6-tool-mounts","name":"6 Tool Mounts","source":"published"}],"sensors":[],"integratedSystems":[{"id":"internal-comlink","name":"Internal Comlink","source":"published"}],"accessories":[{"id":"diagnostics-package","name":"Diagnostics Package","source":"published"},{"id":"scomp-link","name":"Scomp Link","source":"published"}],"weapons":[],"sourceText":"Tracked Locomotion, Heuristic Processor , 1 Claw Appendage, 6 Tool Mounts, Diagnostics Package , Internal Comlink , Scomp Link","sourcePossessions":"Holorecorder , Tool Kit , Astrogation Buffer (Storage Device, 5 Memory Units) Availability: Licensed ; Cost: 8,625 credits Abilities [ ] Focused Repairs: The S19 Astromech Droid can reduce the time needed for repairs by making a Mechanics check. For every point by which the check result exceeds the DC, the time needed to make repairs is reduced by 2 minutes. The amount of time needed to complete repairs cannot be reduced to less than 10 minutes. S19 Astromech Droid Protocol Format [ ] See also: Protocol Format Small 2nd-Degree Droid Hit Points: 4 Damage Threshold : 10 System Actions [ ] Move (1 Swift Action , 2/Turn) [ ] The S19 Astromech Droid moves 4 squares ( Tracked ). Focused Repairs (1 Swift Action , 2/Turn) [ ] The S19 Astromech Droid can make a Mechanics check to assist its master with repairs to any damaged or disabled Droid or device. If the check is successful, the Droid's master can reroll his or her Mechanics check but must accept the second result, even if it is worse. Jury-Rig (2 Swift Actions , 1/Turn) [ ] The S19 Astromech Droid makes a DC 25 Mechanics check to make temporary repairs to any disabled mechanical or electronic device (see Jury-Rig ). Recharge Shields (2 Swift Actions , 1/Turn) [ ] The S19 Astromech Droid makes a DC 20 Mechanics check. If the check is successful, the Vehicle regains 5 SR, up to its normal maximum. Regulate Power (2 Swift Actions , 1/Turn) [ ] The S19 Astromech Droid makes a DC 20 Mechanics check. If the check is successful, the Vehicle moves +1 step on on Condition Track . Run Diagnostics (1 Swift Action , 1/Turn) [ ] The S19 Astromech Droid aids a character's Mechanics check, providing a +2 bonus to the check. Base Stats [ ]"},"cl":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"swse":{"speedText":"4 Squares ( Tracked )","droidSystemText":"Tracked Locomotion, Heuristic Processor , 1 Claw Appendage, 6 Tool Mounts, Diagnostics Package , Internal Comlink , Scomp Link"}}}
