{"_id":"52995c4bc843714c","name":"DSD1_Dwarf_Spider_Droid","type":"droid","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","system":{"degree":"4th-Degree","initiative":null,"senses":"Perception","perception":17,"reflexDefense":13,"flatFooted":13,"fortitudeDefense":16,"willDefense":11,"HP":32,"damageThreshold":26,"speed":8,"baseAttackBonus":null,"grapple":null,"attacks":{"melee":[],"ranged":[{"name":"Blaster Cannon","bonus":5,"damage":"3d12, 1-Square Splash"},{"name":"Blaster Cannon","bonus":5,"damage":"3d12, 1-Square Splash"}]},"baseStats":{"abilities":{"strength":22,"dexterity":9,"intelligence":10,"wisdom":12,"charisma":8,"constitution":0}},"skills":{"Climb":10,"Perception":17},"type":"droid","description":"","costNumeric":15000,"category":"droid","cost":15000,"droidDegreeKey":"4th-degree","droidRole":"battle","droidRoleLabel":"Battle","droidSystemText":"Walking Locomotion, Climbing Claws , Extra Legs , Magnetic Feet , Remote Receiver , Synchronized Fire Circuits , 1 Claw Appendage, 1 Tool Mount, Darkvision , Improved Sensor Package , Locked Access","droidSystems":{"processor":{"id":"remote-receiver","name":"Remote Receiver","source":"published"},"locomotion":[{"id":"walking-locomotion","name":"Walking Locomotion","source":"published"}],"appendages":[{"id":"1-claw-appendage","name":"1 Claw Appendage","source":"published"},{"id":"1-tool-mount","name":"1 Tool Mount","source":"published"}],"sensors":[{"id":"darkvision","name":"Darkvision","source":"published"},{"id":"improved-sensor-package","name":"Improved Sensor Package","source":"published"}],"integratedSystems":[{"id":"locked-access","name":"Locked Access","source":"published"}],"accessories":[{"id":"climbing-claws","name":"Climbing Claws","source":"published"},{"id":"extra-legs","name":"Extra Legs","source":"published"},{"id":"magnetic-feet","name":"Magnetic Feet","source":"published"},{"id":"synchronized-fire-circuits","name":"Synchronized Fire Circuits","source":"published"}],"weapons":[{"id":"blaster-cannon","name":"Blaster Cannon","mode":"ranged","damage":"3d12, 1-Square Splash","attackBonus":5,"source":"published-attack"},{"id":"blaster-cannon","name":"Blaster Cannon","mode":"ranged","damage":"3d12, 1-Square Splash","attackBonus":5,"source":"published-attack"}],"sourceText":"Walking Locomotion, Climbing Claws , Extra Legs , Magnetic Feet , Remote Receiver , Synchronized Fire Circuits , 1 Claw Appendage, 1 Tool Mount, Darkvision , Improved Sensor Package , Locked Access","sourcePossessions":"Blaster Cannon , Quadanium Plating ( Droid Armor ; +5 Reflex ) Availability: Military ; Cost: 15,000 credits DSD1 Dwarf Spider Droid Protocol Format [ ] Reference Book: Star Wars Saga Edition Scavenger's Guide to Droids See also: Protocol Format Large 4th-Degree Droid Hit Points: 32 Damage Threshold : 26 System Actions [ ] Move (1 Swift Action , 2/Turn) [ ] The DSD1 Dwarf Spider Droid moves 8 squares ( Walking ) or 4 squares (Climbing). Blaster Cannon Attack (1 Swift Action , 1/Turn) [ ] The DSD1 Dwarf Spider Droid makes a ranged attack at +5. If successful, the attack deals 3d12 points of damage as an Area Attack that also has the chance to hit enemies adjacent to the target. If unsuccessful, the attack deals half damage to the target and no damage to enemies adjacent to the target. Crush (1 Swift Action , 1/Turn) [ ] The DSD1 Dwarf Spider Droid makes a melee attack at +8. If successful, the attack deals 1d6+10 points of damage. Patrol Duty (1 Swift Action , 1/Turn) [ ] The DSD1 Dwarf Spider Droid makes a Perception check against a target's Stealth check. If the check is successful, the Dwarf Spider Droid detects the target. Stability (1 Free Action ) [ ] The DSD1 Dwarf Spider Droid receives a +5 bonus to avoid being knocked Prone . Base Stats [ ]"},"cl":3},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"swse":{"speedText":"8 Squares ( Walking ), 4 Squares (Climbing); Magnetic Feet","droidSystemText":"Walking Locomotion, Climbing Claws , Extra Legs , Magnetic Feet , Remote Receiver , Synchronized Fire Circuits , 1 Claw Appendage, 1 Tool Mount, Darkvision , Improved Sensor Package , Locked Access"}}}
