ed"},{"id":"vocabulator","name":"Vocabulator","source":"published"}],"accessories":[],"weapons":[{"id":"heavy-repeating-blaster","name":"Heavy Repeating Blaster","mode":"ranged","damage":"3d10+3, 2-Square Autofire","attackBonus":7,"source":"published-attack"},{"id":"heavy-repeating-blaster","name":"Heavy Repeating Blaster","mode":"ranged","damage":"4d10+3, 2-Square Autofire","attackBonus":5,"source":"published-attack"},{"id":"ion-rifle","name":"Ion Rifle","mode":"ranged","damage":"3d8+3 ( Ion","attackBonus":7,"source":"published-attack"},{"id":"ion-rifle","name":"Ion Rifle","mode":"ranged","damage":"4d8+3 ( Ion","attackBonus":5,"source":"published-attack"},{"id":"needler","name":"Needler","mode":"ranged","damage":"2d4+3, See Below","attackBonus":7,"source":"published-attack"},{"id":"missile-launcher","name":"Missile Launcher","mode":"ranged","damage":"6d6+3, 2-Square Burst","attackBonus":7,"source":"published-attack"}],"sourceText":"Tracked Locomotion, Basic Processor , 2 Claw Appendages, 2 Tool Mounts ( Multifunction Apparatus ), Darkvision , Improved Sensor Package , Locked Access , Vocabulator","sourcePossessions":"Heavy Repeating Blaster , Ion Rifle , Missile Launcher (6 Hunter-Seeker Missiles), Needler , Neutronium Plating ( Droid Armor ; +11 Reflex ) Availability: Military ; Cost: 28,535 credits Abilities [ ] Hunter-Seeker Missiles: When the E522 Assassin Droid attacks with its Missile Launcher , the missile locks on a chosen target and permits the Droid to make an attack roll once per round until the missile either hits the intended target or misses for five consecutive rounds. Neurotoxin Darts: On a successful attack with the Needler on a living creature, the target is injected with a Paralytic Poison . E522 Assassin Droid Protocol Format [ ] See also: Protocol Format Medium 4th-Degree Droid Hit Points: 74 Damage Threshold : 23 System Actions [ ] Move (1 Swift Action , 2/Turn) [ ] The E522 Assassin Droid moves 6 squares ( Tracked ). Cover Fire (1 Swift Action , 1/Turn) [ ] When the E522 Assassin Droid makes a successful ranged attack, all of its allies within 6 squares of the Droid gain a +1 bonus to their Reflex Defense : until the start of the Droid's next turn . Paralyze Opponent (1 Swift Action , 1/Turn) [ ] When the E522 Assassin Droid makes a successful ranged attack with its Needler , the Droid can paralyze an opponent with Paralytic Poison . Rapid Shot (1 Swift Action , 1/Turn) [ ] The E522 Assassin Droid makes a ranged attack at +5 with either its Heavy Repeating Blaster or its Ion Rifle . If successful, the attack deals either 4d10+3 points of damage or 4d8+3 points of Ion damage, depending on the weapon used. Base Stats [ ]"},"cl":7},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"swse":{"speedText":"6 Squares ( Tracked )","droidSystemText":"Tracked Locomotion, Basic Processor , 2 Claw Appendages, 2 Tool Mounts ( Multifunction Apparatus ), Darkvision , Improved Sensor Package , Locked Access , Vocabulator"}}}
{"_id":"57f7b1bec812e3a5","name":"GY-I_Information_Analysis_Droid","type":"droid","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","system":{"degree":"3rd-Degree","initiative":6,"senses":"Perception","perception":9,"reflexDefense":13,"flatFooted":12,"fortitudeDefense":10,"willDefense":15,"HP":18,"damageThreshold":10,"speed":6,"baseAttackBonus":null,"grapple":null,"attacks":{"melee":[{"name":"Unarmed","bonus":-1,"damage":"1d3-1"}],"ranged":[]},"baseStats":{"abilities":{"strength":8,"dexterity":12,"intelligence":15,"wisdom":15,"charisma":16,"constitution":0}},"skills":{"Deception":8,"Gather Information":13,"Initiative":6,"Perception":9,"Use Computer":7},"type":"droid","description":"","costNumeric":11855,"category":"droid","cost":11855,"droidDegreeKey":"3rd-degree","droidRole":"information","droidRoleLabel":"Information","droidSystemText":"Walking Locomotion, Heuristic Processor , 2 Hand Appendages, Improved Sensor Package , Vocabulator Availability: Licensed ; Cost: 11,855 credits GY-I Information Analysis Droid Protocol Format [ ] See also: Protocol Format Medium 3rd-Degree Droid Hit Points: 18 Damage Threshold : 10 System Actions [ ] Move (1 Swift Action , 2/Turn) [ ] The GY-I Information Analysis Droid moves 6 squares ( Walking ). Analyze Data (1 Swift Action , 1/Turn) [ ] The GY-I Information Analysis Droid assists a character's Gather Information check, providing a +2 bonus to the check. Diagnosis ( Free Action ) [ ] The GY-I Information Analysis Droid makes a Knowledge (Life Sciences) check with a +5 bonus to determine a source of disease or injury and communicates the diagnosis to its owner. Expert Opinion (1 Swift Action ) [ ] The GY-I Information Analysis Droid makes a Knowledge (Life Sciences) , Knowledge (Galactic Lore) , or Knowledge (Physical Sciences) check and reports its findings. Base Stats [ ] Skills : Deception +8, Gather Information +13, Initiative +6, Knowledge (Galactic Lore) +7, Knowledge (Life Sciences) +7, Knowledge (Physical Sciences) +7, Perception +9, Us