{"_id":"58de8bb1bee46be5","name":"8D_Smelter_Droid","type":"droid","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","system":{"degree":"5th-Degree","initiative":null,"senses":"Perception","perception":2,"reflexDefense":15,"flatFooted":15,"fortitudeDefense":14,"willDefense":10,"HP":4,"damageThreshold":14,"speed":6,"baseAttackBonus":null,"grapple":null,"attacks":{"melee":[{"name":"Unarmed","bonus":2,"damage":"1d4+4"},{"name":"Unarmed","bonus":2,"damage":"2d4+4"}],"ranged":[]},"baseStats":{"abilities":{"strength":18,"dexterity":10,"intelligence":8,"wisdom":10,"charisma":8,"constitution":0}},"skills":{"Endurance":14,"Perception":2},"type":"droid","description":"","costNumeric":7250,"category":"droid","cost":7250,"droidDegreeKey":"5th-degree","droidRole":"mining","droidRoleLabel":"Mining","droidSystemText":"Walking Locomotion, Basic Processor , 2 Claw Appendages, Improved Sensor Package , Darkvision , Secondary Battery , Vocabulator","droidSystems":{"processor":{"id":"basic-processor","name":"Basic Processor","source":"published"},"locomotion":[{"id":"walking-locomotion","name":"Walking Locomotion","source":"published"}],"appendages":[{"id":"2-claw-appendages","name":"2 Claw Appendages","source":"published"}],"sensors":[{"id":"improved-sensor-package","name":"Improved Sensor Package","source":"published"},{"id":"darkvision","name":"Darkvision","source":"published"}],"integratedSystems":[{"id":"secondary-battery","name":"Secondary Battery","source":"published"},{"id":"vocabulator","name":"Vocabulator","source":"published"}],"accessories":[],"weapons":[],"sourceText":"Walking Locomotion, Basic Processor , 2 Claw Appendages, Improved Sensor Package , Darkvision , Secondary Battery , Vocabulator","sourcePossessions":"Duravlex Shell ( Droid Armor ; +4 Reflex ) Availability: Licensed ; Cost: 7,250 credits Abilities [ ] Heat Resistant: When the 8D Smelter Droid is exposed to Extreme Heat or Fire , it takes half damage if the attack succeeds, or no damage if the attack fails, and it does not move on the Condition Track . 8D Smelter Droid Protocol Format [ ] See also: Protocol Format Medium 5th-Degree Droid Hit Points: 4 Damage Threshold : 14 System Actions [ ] Move (1 Swift Action , 2/Turn) [ ] The 8D Smelter Droid moves 4 squares ( Walking ). Mighty Swing (1 Swift Action , 1/Turn) [ ] The 8D Smelter Droid deals +1 die of damage on its next melee attack in the same round. Base Stats [ ]"},"cl":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"swse":{"speedText":"6 Squares ( Walking )","droidSystemText":"Walking Locomotion, Basic Processor , 2 Claw Appendages, Improved Sensor Package , Darkvision , Secondary Battery , Vocabulator"}}}
{"_id":"58ff485d198fa06f","name":"PG-5_Gunnery_Droid","type":"droid","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","system":{"degree":"2nd-Degree","initiative":null,"senses":"Perception","perception":8,"reflexDefense":8,"flatFooted":8,"fortitudeDefense":15,"willDefense":10,"HP":15,"damageThreshold":20,"speed":4,"baseAttackBonus":null,"grapple":null,"attacks":{"melee":[{"name":"Unarmed","bonus":6,"damage":"1d6+5"}],"ranged":[{"name":"Laser Welder","bonus":0,"damage":"3d6"},{"name":"Laser Welder","bonus":0,"damage":"3d6"}]},"baseStats":{"abilities":{"strength":20,"dexterity":8,"intelligence":14,"wisdom":11,"charisma":6,"constitution":0}},"skills":{"Mechanics":13,"Perception":8,"Use Computer":13},"type":"droid","description":"","costNumeric":7280,"category":"droid","cost":7280,"droidDegreeKey":"2nd-degree","droidRole":"gunnery","droidRoleLabel":"Gunnery","droidSystemText":"Wheeled Locomotion, Heuristic Processor , 1 Claw Appendage, 3 Tool Mounts, Diagnostics Package , Improved Sensor Package , Scomp Link","droidSystems":{"processor":{"id":"heuristic-processor","name":"Heuristic Processor","source":"published"},"locomotion":[{"id":"wheeled-locomotion","name":"Wheeled Locomotion","source":"published"}],"appendages":[{"id":"1-claw-appendage","name":"1 Claw Appendage","source":"published"},{"id":"3-tool-mounts","name":"3 Tool Mounts","source":"published"}],"sensors":[{"id":"improved-sensor-package","name":"Improved Sensor Package","source":"published"}],"integratedSystems":[],"accessories":[{"id":"diagnostics-package","name":"Diagnostics Package","source":"published"},{"id":"scomp-link","name":"Scomp Link","source":"published"}],"weapons":[{"id":"laser-welder","name":"Laser Welder","mode":"ranged","damage":"3d6","attackBonus":0,"source":"published-attack"},{"id":"laser-welder","name":"Laser Welder","mode":"ranged","damage":"3d6","attackBonus":0,"source":"published-attack"}],"sourceText":"Wheeled Locomotion, Heuristic Processor , 1 Claw Appendage, 3 Tool Mounts, Diagnostics Package , Improved Sensor Package , Scomp Link","sourcePossessions":"Laser Welder Availability: Licensed ; Cost: 7,280 credits Abilities [ ] Battery Fire: The PG-5 Gunnery Droid can control all Weapon Systems that make up a single Battery as if the Droid were controlling only one weapon. However, the Droid takes a -1 penalty to its attack rolls for each weapon in the Battery . Superior Weapon Repair: During the first encounter after the PG-5 Gunnery Droid performs or assists with repairs or upgrades on a Vehicle's Weapon Systems , each weapon gains a +1 bonus to attack rolls. PG-5 Gunnery Droid Protocol Format [ ] See also: Protocol Format Large 2nd-Degree Droid Hit Points: 15 Damage Threshold : 20 System Actions [ ] Move (1 Swift Action , 2/Turn) [ ] The PG-5 Gunnery Droid moves 4 squares ( Wheeled ). Battery Fire (2 Swift Actions , 1/Turn) [ ] The PG-5 Gunnery Droid can control all Weapon Systems that make up a single Battery as if the Droid were controlling only one weapon. However, the Droid takes a -1 penalty to its attack rolls for each weapon in the Battery . Improve Access (2 Swift Actions , 1/Turn) [ ] The R2-Series Astromech Droid makes a Use Computer check against a target computer's Will Defense to improve the computer's Attitude toward it. Jury-Rig (2 Swift Actions , 1/Turn) [ ] The PG-5 Gunnery Droid makes a DC 25 Mechanics check to make temporary repairs to any disabled mechanical or electronic device (see Jury-Rig ). Recharge Shields (2 Swift Actions , 1/Turn) [ ] The PG-5 Gunnery Droid makes a DC 20 Mechanics check. If the check is successful, the Vehicle regains 5 SR, up to its normal maximum. Sensor Sweep (1 Swift Action , 1/Turn) [ ] The PG-5 Gunnery Droid can make a Use Computer check to Use Sensors when linked to the Vehicle's systems. Base Stats [ ]"},"cl":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"swse":{"speedText":"4 Squares ( Wheeled )","droidSystemText":"Wheeled Locomotion, Heuristic Processor , 1 Claw Appendage, 3 To