{"_id":"8b0f82d985ea3401","name":"PLNK-Series_Power_Droid","type":"droid","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","system":{"degree":"5th-Degree","initiative":null,"senses":"Perception","perception":0,"reflexDefense":18,"flatFooted":18,"fortitudeDefense":13,"willDefense":10,"HP":11,"damageThreshold":13,"speed":4,"baseAttackBonus":null,"grapple":null,"attacks":{"melee":[{"name":"Unarmed","bonus":4,"damage":"1d3+2"}],"ranged":[]},"baseStats":{"abilities":{"strength":14,"dexterity":8,"intelligence":8,"wisdom":9,"charisma":4,"constitution":0}},"skills":{"Mechanics":10,"Perception":0},"type":"droid","description":"","costNumeric":6990,"category":"droid","cost":6990,"droidDegreeKey":"5th-degree","droidRole":"construction","droidRoleLabel":"Construction","droidSystemText":"Walking Locomotion, Basic Processor , 2 Tool Mounts, Darkvision , Diagnostics Package","droidSystems":{"processor":{"id":"basic-processor","name":"Basic Processor","source":"published"},"locomotion":[{"id":"walking-locomotion","name":"Walking Locomotion","source":"published"}],"appendages":[{"id":"2-tool-mounts","name":"2 Tool Mounts","source":"published"}],"sensors":[{"id":"darkvision","name":"Darkvision","source":"published"}],"integratedSystems":[],"accessories":[{"id":"diagnostics-package","name":"Diagnostics Package","source":"published"}],"weapons":[],"sourceText":"Walking Locomotion, Basic Processor , 2 Tool Mounts, Darkvision , Diagnostics Package","sourcePossessions":"Liquid Tibana Tank and Pump, LT-Powered Generator, Duranium Plating ( Droid Armor ; +8 Reflex ) Availability: Military ; Cost: 6,990 credits Abilities [ ] Failsafe Withdrawal: The first time a PLNK-Series Power Droid is attacked in an encounter, as a Reaction , it can move up to its speed immediately after that attack is resolved. Power Charge: With a successful DC 15 Mechanics check, a PLNK-Series Power Droid can recharge a depleted blaster Power Pack at a rate of 1 shot per round. Also, when using the Recharge Shields Action, the Droid can restore 7 points to a Vehicle's Shield Rating , up to its normal maximum. PLNK-Series Power Droid Protocol Format [ ] See also: Protocol Format Medium 5th-Degree Droid Hit Points: 11 Damage Threshold : 13 System Actions [ ] Move (1 Swift Action , 2/Turn) [ ] The PLNK-Series Power Droid moves 4 squares ( Walking ). Ammo Source ( Free Action ) [ ] The PLNK-Series Power Droid can be hooked up to some types of repeating blasters and other weapons and used as an ammunition source. Failsafe Withdrawal ( Reaction ) [ ] The first time a PLNK-Series Power Droid is attacked in an encounter, as a Reaction , it can move up to its speed immediately after that attack is resolved. Power Charge (1 Swift Action , 1/Turn) [ ] With a successful DC 15 Mechanics check, a PLNK-Series Power Droid can recharge a depleted blaster Power Pack at a rate of 1 shot per round. Recharge Shields (2 Swift Actions , 1/Turn) [ ] The PLNK-Series Power Droid makes a DC 20 Mechanics check. If the check is successful, the Vehicle regains 7 SR, up to its normal maximum. Regulate Power (2 Swift Actions , 1/Turn) [ ] The PLNK-Series Power Droid makes a DC 20 Mechanics check. If the check is successful, the Vehicle moves +1 step on on Condition Track . Base Stats [ ]"},"cl":1},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"swse":{"speedText":"4 Squares ( Walking ); Failsafe Withdrawal","droidSystemText":"Walking Locomotion, Basic Processor , 2 Tool Mounts, Darkvision , Diagnostics Package"}}}
