ed"}],"integratedSystems":[{"id":"locked-access","name":"Locked Access","source":"published"},{"id":"shield-generator-sr-20","name":"Shield Generator (SR 20)","source":"published"},{"id":"vocabulator","name":"Vocabulator","source":"published"}],"accessories":[{"id":"climbing-claws","name":"Climbing Claws","source":"published"},{"id":"holographic-image-disguiser","name":"Holographic Image Disguiser","source":"published"},{"id":"silence-bubble-generator","name":"Silence-Bubble Generator","source":"published"}],"weapons":[{"id":"vibroblade","name":"Vibroblade","mode":"melee","damage":"2d6+4","attackBonus":13,"source":"published-attack"},{"id":"vibroblade","name":"Vibroblade","mode":"melee","damage":"2d6+4","attackBonus":8,"source":"published-attack"},{"id":"blaster-rifle","name":"Blaster Rifle","mode":"ranged","damage":"3d8","attackBonus":11,"source":"published-attack"},{"id":"blaster-rifle","name":"Blaster Rifle","mode":"ranged","damage":"4d8","attackBonus":9,"source":"published-attack"},{"id":"blaster-rifle","name":"Blaster Rifle","mode":"ranged","damage":"3d8","attackBonus":6,"source":"published-attack"},{"id":"and-blaster-rifle","name":"and Blaster Rifle","mode":"ranged","damage":"3d8","attackBonus":6,"source":"published-attack"},{"id":"blaster-rifle","name":"Blaster Rifle","mode":"ranged","damage":"4d8","attackBonus":4,"source":"published-attack"},{"id":"and-blaster-rifle","name":"and Blaster Rifle","mode":"ranged","damage":"4d8","attackBonus":4,"source":"published-attack"},{"id":"blaster-rifle","name":"Blaster Rifle","mode":"ranged","damage":"3d8","attackBonus":11,"source":"published-attack"},{"id":"blaster-rifle","name":"Blaster Rifle","mode":"ranged","damage":"4d8","attackBonus":9,"source":"published-attack"},{"id":"blaster-rifle","name":"Blaster Rifle","mode":"ranged","damage":"3d8","attackBonus":6,"source":"published-attack"},{"id":"blaster-rifle","name":"Blaster Rifle","mode":"ranged","damage":"4d8","attackBonus":4,"source":"published-attack"}],"sourceText":"Walking Locomotion, Climbing Claws , Heuristic Processor , 4 Tool Mounts, Darkvision , Holographic Image Disguiser , Improved Sensor Package , Locked Access , Shield Generator (SR 20), Silence-Bubble Generator , Vocabulator","sourcePossessions":"Blaster Rifle (2), Vibroblade (2), Liquid Cable Dispenser , Bronzium Shell (As Quadanium Plating; Droid Armor ; +5 Reflex ) Availability: Military ; Cost: 33,720 credits Abilities [ ] Penetrate Hull: An Infiltrator-Series Droid always rolls maximum damage when using its Vibroblades to cut into the hull of a Vehicle or to cut through solid walls and doors Infiltrator-Series Droid Protocol Format [ ] See also: Protocol Format Medium 4th-Degree Droid Hit Points: 40 Damage Threshold : 14 (SR 20) System Actions [ ] Move (1 Swift Action , 2/Turn) [ ] The Infiltrator-Series Droid moves 6 squares ( Walking ) or 3 squares (Climbing). Create a Diversion to Hide (1 Swift Action , 1/Turn) [ ] The Infiltrator-Series Droid can make a Deception check to Create a Diversion to Hide and give the Infiltrator time to hide. Penetrate Hull (2 Swift Actions , 1/Turn) [ ] The Infiltrator-Series Droid makes a melee attack at +13. If successful, the attack deals 2d6+4 points of damage, or 16 points of damage against the hull of a Vehicle or against solid walls and doors. Rapid Shot (1 Swift Action , 1/Turn) [ ] The Infiltrator-Series Droid makes a ranged attack at +9. If successful, the attack deals 4d8 points of damage. Sneak (1 Swift Action , 1/Turn) [ ] The Infiltrator-Series Droid can slip past an opponent without being noticed by making a successful Stealth check opposed by the opponent's Perception check. Snipe (1 Swift Action , 1/Turn) [ ] The Infiltrator-Series Droid can attempt to hide again with a Stealth check after making a ranged attack from hiding. Base Stats [ ]"},"cl":4},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"swse":{"speedText":"6 Squares ( Walking ), 3 Squares (Climbing)","droidSystemText":"Walking Locomotion, Climbing Claws , Heuristic Processor , 4 Tool Mounts, Darkvision , Holographic Image Disguiser , Improved Sensor Package , Locked Access , Shield Generator (SR 20), Silence-Bubble Generator , Vocabulator"}}}
