{"_id":"9a23cbfa06eeb7ef","name":"AS23_Aerial_Survey_Droid","type":"droid","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","system":{"degree":"3rd-Degree","initiative":null,"senses":"Perception","perception":14,"reflexDefense":15,"flatFooted":11,"fortitudeDefense":9,"willDefense":12,"HP":3,"damageThreshold":9,"speed":9,"baseAttackBonus":null,"grapple":null,"attacks":{"melee":[],"ranged":[]},"baseStats":{"abilities":{"strength":8,"dexterity":18,"intelligence":12,"wisdom":14,"charisma":7,"constitution":0}},"skills":{"Perception":14,"Pilot":14,"Survival":12},"type":"droid","description":"","costNumeric":23500,"category":"droid","cost":23500,"droidDegreeKey":"3rd-degree","droidRole":"information","droidRoleLabel":"Information","droidSystemText":"Flying Locomotion, Basic Processor , Automap , Darkvision , Improved Sensor Package , Internal Comlink Availability: Licensed ; Cost: 23,500 credits Abilities [ ] Spotter: When in flight, the AS23 Aerial Survey Droid can use its observation skills to locate enemy targets and relay their locations back to its master to assist in targeting for long-range and artillery weapons. Any attacks against targets spotted by the Droid ignore all Concealment and reduce Cover by 1 step; for example, Total Cover becomes Improved Cover . AS23 Aerial Survey Droid Protocol Format [ ] See also: Protocol Format Small 3rd-Degree Droid Hit Points: 3 Damage Threshold : 9 System Actions [ ] Move (1 Swift Action , 2/Turn) [ ] The AS23 Aerial Survey Droid moves 9 squares ( Flying ). Engage the Enemy ( Free Action ) [ ] The AS23 Aerial Survey Droid makes a Pilot check instead of an Initiative check at the start of a battle. Know Direction (3 Swift Actions , 1/Turn) [ ] With a DC 10 Survival check, the AS23 Aerial Survey Droid can determine which direction is north while planetside. Spotter (2 Swift Actions , 1/Turn) [ ] The AS23 Aerial Survey Droid can locate targets and relay their locations to its master, reducing the targets' Cover by 1 step and ignoring Concealment . Base Stats [ ] Skills : Perception +14, Pilot +14, Survival +12 Vital Systems: Automap , Darkvision , Internal Comlink","droidSystems":{"processor":{"id":"basic-processor","name":"Basic Processor","source":"published"},"locomotion":[{"id":"flying-locomotion","name":"Flying Locomotion","source":"published"}],"appendages":[],"sensors":[{"id":"darkvision","name":"Darkvision","source":"published"},{"id":"improved-sensor-package","name":"Improved Sensor Package","source":"published"},{"id":"darkvision","name":"Darkvision","source":"published"}],"integratedSystems":[{"id":"internal-comlink-availability-licensed-cost-23","name":"Internal Comlink Availability: Licensed ; Cost: 23","source":"published"},{"id":"internal-comlink","name":"Internal Comlink","source":"published"}],"accessories":[{"id":"automap","name":"Automap","source":"published"},{"id":"500-credits-abilities-spotter-when-in-flight","name":"500 credits Abilities [ ] Spotter: When in flight","source":"published"},{"id":"the-as23-aerial-survey-droid-can-use-its-observation-skills-to-locate-enemy-targets-and-relay-their-locations-back-to-its-master-to-assist-in-targeting-for-long-range-and-artillery-weapons-any-attacks-against-targets-spotted-by-the-droid-ignore-all-concealment-and-reduce-cover-by-1-step-for-example","name":"the AS23 Aerial Survey Droid can use its observation skills to locate enemy targets and relay their locations back to its master to assist in targeting for long-range and artillery weapons. Any attacks against targets spotted by the Droid ignore all Concealment and reduce Cover by 1 step; for example","source":"published"},{"id":"total-cover-becomes-improved-cover-as23-aerial-survey-droid-protocol-format-see-also-protocol-format-small-3rd-degree-droid-hit-points-3-damage-threshold-9-system-actions-move-1-swift-action-2-turn-the-as23-aerial-survey-droid-moves-9-squares-flying-engage-the-enemy-free-action-the-as23-aerial-survey-droid-makes-a-pilot-check-instead-of-an-initiative-check-at-the-start-of-a-battle-know-direction-3-swift-actions-1-turn-with-a-dc-10-survival-check","name":"Total Cover becomes Improved Cover . AS23 Aerial Survey Droid Protocol Format [ ] See also: Protocol Format Small 3rd-Degree Droid Hit Points: 3 Damage Threshold : 9 System Actions [ ] Move (1 Swift Action, 2/Turn) [ ] The AS23 Aerial Survey Droid moves 9 squares ( Flying ). Engage the Enemy ( Free Action ) [ ] The AS23 Aerial Survey Droid makes a Pilot check instead of an Initiative check at the start of a battle. Know Direction (3 Swift Actions, 1/Turn) [ ] With a DC 10 Survival check","source":"published"},{"id":"the-as23-aerial-survey-droid-can-determine-which-direction-is-north-while-planetside-spotter-2-swift-actions-1-turn-the-as23-aerial-survey-droid-can-locate-targets-and-relay-their-locations-to-its-master","name":"the AS23 Aerial Survey Droid can determine which direction is north while planetside. Spotter (2 Swift Actions, 1/Turn) [ ] The AS23 Aerial Survey Droid can locate targets and relay their locations to its master","source":"published"},{"id":"reducing-the-targets-cover-by-1-step-and-ignoring-concealment-base-stats-skills-perception-14","name":"reducing the targets' Cover by 1 step and ignoring Concealment . Base Stats [ ] Skills : Perception +14","source":"published"},{"id":"pilot-14","name":"Pilot +14","source":"published"},{"id":"survival-12-vital-systems-automap","name":"Survival +12 Vital Systems: Automap","source":"published"}],"weapons":[],"sourceText":"Flying Locomotion, Basic Processor , Automap , Darkvision , Improved Sensor Package , Internal Comlink Availability: Licensed ; Cost: 23,500 credits Abilities [ ] Spotter: When in flight, the AS23 Aerial Survey Droid can use its observation skills to locate enemy targets and relay their locations back to its master to assist in targeting for long-range and artillery weapons. Any attacks against targets spotted by the Droid ignore all Concealment and reduce Cover by 1 step; for example, Total Cover becomes Improved Cover . AS23 Aerial Survey Droid Protocol Format [ ] See also: Protocol Format Small 3rd-Degree Droid Hit Points: 3 Damage Threshold : 9 System Actions [ ] Move (1 Swift Action , 2/Turn) [ ] The AS23 Aerial Survey Droid moves 9 squares ( Flying ). Engage the Enemy ( Free Action ) [ ] The AS23 Aerial Survey Droid makes a Pilot check instead of an Initiative check at the start of a battle. Know Direction (3 Swift Actions , 1/Turn) [ ] With a DC 10 Survival check, the AS23 Aerial Survey Droid can determine which direction is north while planetside. Spotter (2 Swift Actions , 1/Turn) [ ] The AS23 Aerial Survey Droid can locate targets and relay their locations to its master, reducing the targets' Cover by 1 step and ignoring Concealment . Base Stats [ ] Skills : Perception +14, Pilot +14, Survival +12 Vital Systems: Automap , Darkvision , Internal Comlink"},"cl":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"swse":{"speedText":"9 Squares ( Flying )","droidSystemText":"Flying Locomotion, Basic Processor , Automap , Darkvision , Improved Sensor Package , Internal Comlink Availability: Licensed ; Cost: 23,500 credits Abilities [ ] Spotter: When in flight, the AS23 Aerial Survey Droid can use its observation skills to locate enemy targets and relay their locations back to its master to assist in targeting for long-range and artillery weapons. Any attacks against targets spotted by the Droid ignore all Concealment and reduce Cover by 1 step; for example, Total Cover becomes Improved Cover . AS23 Aerial Survey Droid Protocol Format [ ] See also: Protocol Format Small 3rd-Degree Droid Hit Points: 3 Damage Threshold : 9 System Actions [ ] Move (1 Swift Action , 2/Turn) [ ] The AS23 Aerial Survey Droid moves 9 squares ( Flying ). Engage the Enemy ( Free Action ) [ ] The AS23 Aerial Survey Droid makes a Pilot check instead of an Initiative check at the start of a battle. Know Direction (3 Swift Actions , 1/Turn) [ ] With a DC 10 Survival check, the AS23 Aerial Survey Droid can determine which direction is north while planetside. Spotter (2 Swift Actions , 1/Turn) [ ] The AS23 Aerial Survey Droid can locate targets and relay their locations to its master, reducing the targets' Cover by 1 step and ignoring Concealment . Base Stats [ ] Skills : Perception +14, Pilot +14, Survival +12 Vital Systems: Automap , Darkvision , Internal Comlink"}}}
