"published-attack"},{"id":"blaster-rifle","name":"Blaster Rifle","mode":"ranged","damage":"5d8+4","attackBonus":8,"source":"published-attack"},{"id":"blaster-rifle","name":"Blaster Rifle","mode":"ranged","damage":"3d8+4","attackBonus":3,"source":"published-attack"},{"id":"and-blaster-rifle","name":"and Blaster Rifle","mode":"ranged","damage":"3d8+4","attackBonus":3,"source":"published-attack"},{"id":"blaster-rifle","name":"Blaster Rifle","mode":"ranged","damage":"3d8+4","attackBonus":8,"source":"published-attack"},{"id":"blaster-rifle","name":"Blaster Rifle","mode":"ranged","damage":"5d8+4","attackBonus":8,"source":"published-attack"},{"id":"blaster-rifle","name":"Blaster Rifle","mode":"ranged","damage":"3d8+4","attackBonus":3,"source":"published-attack"}],"sourceText":"Walking Locomotion, Heuristic Processor , 2 Tool Mounts, Darkvision , Improved Sensor Package , Locked Access , Vocabulator","sourcePossessions":"Blaster Rifle (2), Quadanium Battle Armor ( Droid Armor ; +7 Reflex ) Availability: Restricted ; Cost: 19,865 credits Abilities [ ] Blaster Surge: As a Full-Round Action , the HK-77 Assassin Droid can forgo its normal attacks to fire a high-powered blaster bolt from one of its rifles. The high-powered bolt deals 5d8+4 points of damage and consumes an additional five shots from the weapon's Power Pack . The weapon cannot be fired during the next round, while it cools down. HK-77 Assassin Droid Protocol Format [ ] See also: Protocol Format Medium 4th-Degree Droid Hit Points: 55 Damage Threshold : 18 System Actions [ ] Move (1 Swift Action , 2/Turn) [ ] The HK-77 Assassin Droid moves 6 squares ( Walking ). Avoid Surprise (1 Free Action ) [ ] The HK-77 Assassin Droid makes a Perception check at the start of a battle. If the check is successful, the Droid's master avoids Surprise . Blaster Surge (1 Swift Action , 1/Turn) [ ] The HK-77 Assassin Droid makes a ranged attack at +8. If successful, the attack deals 5d8+4 points of damage. Salvo (2 Swift Actions , 1/Turn) [ ] The HK-77 Assassin Droid makes two ranged attacks at +3 each. Each successful attack deals 3d8+4 points of damage. Support Fire (1 Swift Action , 1/Turn) [ ] The HK-77 Assassin Droid makes a ranged attack at +8. If successful, the attack deals 3d8+4 points of damage. Base Stats [ ]"},"cl":4},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"swse":{"speedText":"6 Squares ( Walking )","droidSystemText":"Walking Locomotion, Heuristic Processor , 2 Tool Mounts, Darkvision , Improved Sensor Package , Locked Access , Vocabulator"}}}
