{"_id":"cb4623db84f6191e","name":"H-1ME_Battle_Mechanic_Droid","type":"droid","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","system":{"degree":"2nd-Degree","initiative":8,"senses":"Perception","perception":0,"reflexDefense":17,"flatFooted":14,"fortitudeDefense":11,"willDefense":11,"HP":24,"damageThreshold":11,"speed":4,"baseAttackBonus":null,"grapple":null,"attacks":{"melee":[{"name":"Unarmed","bonus":-1,"damage":"1d2-1"}],"ranged":[]},"baseStats":{"abilities":{"strength":8,"dexterity":16,"intelligence":17,"wisdom":11,"charisma":11,"constitution":0}},"skills":{"Initiative":8,"Jump":4,"Mechanics":13,"Perception":0,"Pilot":8,"Stealth":13,"Use Computer":12},"type":"droid","description":"","costNumeric":10565,"category":"droid","cost":10565,"droidDegreeKey":"2nd-degree","droidRole":"repair","droidRoleLabel":"Repair","droidSystemText":"Walking Locomotion, Extra Legs , Magnetic Feet , Heuristic Processor , 8 Tool Mounts, Collapsible Construction , Communications Countermeasures , Vocabulator","droidSystems":{"processor":{"id":"heuristic-processor","name":"Heuristic Processor","source":"published"},"locomotion":[{"id":"walking-locomotion","name":"Walking Locomotion","source":"published"}],"appendages":[{"id":"8-tool-mounts","name":"8 Tool Mounts","source":"published"}],"sensors":[],"integratedSystems":[{"id":"vocabulator","name":"Vocabulator","source":"published"}],"accessories":[{"id":"extra-legs","name":"Extra Legs","source":"published"},{"id":"magnetic-feet","name":"Magnetic Feet","source":"published"},{"id":"collapsible-construction","name":"Collapsible Construction","source":"published"},{"id":"communications-countermeasures","name":"Communications Countermeasures","source":"published"}],"weapons":[],"sourceText":"Walking Locomotion, Extra Legs , Magnetic Feet , Heuristic Processor , 8 Tool Mounts, Collapsible Construction , Communications Countermeasures , Vocabulator","sourcePossessions":"Tool Kit Availability: Restricted ; Cost: 10,565 credits Abilities [ ] Preventative Maintenance: For every 8 hours the H-1ME Battle Mechanic Droid spends working on a Vehicle , the Vehicle regains a number of Hit Points equal to its Challenge Level, up to its maximum number of Hit Points. Preventive Maintenance can occur while a ship is in Hyperspace. H-1ME Battle Mechanic Droid Protocol Format [ ] See also: Protocol Format Small 2nd-Degree Droid Hit Points: 24 Damage Threshold : 11 System Actions [ ] Move (1 Swift Action , 2/Turn) [ ] The H-1ME Battle Mechanic Droid moves 4 squares ( Walking ). Identify Technology (1 Swift Action ) [ ] The H-1ME Battle Mechanic Droid makes a Knowledge (Technology) check and reports its findings. Mechanical Assistance (1 Swift Action , 1/Turn) [ ] The H-1ME Battle Mechanic Droid aids a character's Mechanics check, providing a +2 bonus to the check. Pick Pocket (1 Swift Action , 1/Turn) [ ] The H-1ME Battle Mechanic Droid makes a Stealth check against a target's Perception ; the target receives a +5 bonus to the check. If the check succeeds, the Droid steals from the target an object that is Tiny sized or smaller. Recharge Shields (2 Swift Actions , 1/Turn) [ ] The H-1ME Battle Mechanic Droid makes a DC 20 Mechanics check. If the check is successful, the Vehicle regains 5 SR, up to its normal maximum. Regulate Power (2 Swift Actions , 1/Turn) [ ] The H-1ME Battle Mechanic Droid makes a DC 20 Mechanics check. If the check is successful, the Vehicle moves +1 step on on Condition Track . Base Stats [ ]"},"cl":1},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"swse":{"speedText":"4 Squares ( Walking ); Magnetic Feet","droidSystemText":"Walking Locomotion, Extra Legs , Magnetic Feet , Heuristic Processor , 8 Tool Mounts, Collapsible Construction , Communications Countermeasures , Vocabulator"}}}
