 Squares ( Walking )","droidSystemText":"Walking Locomotion, Basic Processor , 2 Claw Appendages, 2 Tool Mounts"}}}
{"_id":"d6500d615e92ae16","name":"SD-X_Stealth_Battle_Droid","type":"droid","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","system":{"degree":"4th-Degree","initiative":11,"senses":"Perception","perception":13,"reflexDefense":28,"flatFooted":24,"fortitudeDefense":24,"willDefense":21,"HP":68,"damageThreshold":24,"speed":6,"baseAttackBonus":null,"grapple":null,"attacks":{"melee":[{"name":"Unarmed","bonus":10,"damage":"1d6+7"},{"name":"Vibrodagger","bonus":10,"damage":"4d4+7"}],"ranged":[{"name":"Blaster Rifle","bonus":9,"damage":"3d8+4"},{"name":"Blaster Rifle","bonus":9,"damage":"3d8+4"}]},"baseStats":{"abilities":{"strength":16,"dexterity":14,"intelligence":12,"wisdom":14,"charisma":10,"constitution":0}},"skills":{"Initiative":11,"Jump":12,"Mechanics":10,"Perception":13,"Stealth":11},"type":"droid","description":"","costNumeric":25705,"category":"droid","cost":25705,"droidDegreeKey":"4th-degree","droidRole":"infiltration","droidRoleLabel":"Infiltration","droidSystemText":"Walking Locomotion, Heuristic Processor , 2 Hand Appendages, Darkvision , Improved Sensor Package , Internal Comlink (Encrypted), Locked Access , Vocabulator","droidSystems":{"processor":{"id":"heuristic-processor","name":"Heuristic Processor","source":"published"},"locomotion":[{"id":"walking-locomotion","name":"Walking Locomotion","source":"published"}],"appendages":[{"id":"2-hand-appendages","name":"2 Hand Appendages","source":"published"}],"sensors":[{"id":"darkvision","name":"Darkvision","source":"published"},{"id":"improved-sensor-package","name":"Improved Sensor Package","source":"published"}],"integratedSystems":[{"id":"internal-comlink-encrypted","name":"Internal Comlink (Encrypted)","source":"published"},{"id":"locked-access","name":"Locked Access","source":"published"},{"id":"vocabulator","name":"Vocabulator","source":"published"}],"accessories":[],"weapons":[{"id":"vibrodagger","name":"Vibrodagger","mode":"melee","damage":"4d4+7","attackBonus":10,"source":"published-attack"},{"id":"blaster-rifle","name":"Blaster Rifle","mode":"ranged","damage":"3d8+4","attackBonus":9,"source":"published-attack"},{"id":"blaster-rifle","name":"Blaster Rifle","mode":"ranged","damage":"3d8+4","attackBonus":9,"source":"published-attack"}],"sourceText":"Walking Locomotion, Heuristic Processor , 2 Hand Appendages, Darkvision , Improved Sensor Package , Internal Comlink (Encrypted), Locked Access , Vocabulator","sourcePossessions":"Blaster Rifle , Vibrodagger (2), Laminanium Heavy Plating ( Droid Armor ; +12 Reflex ) Availability: Military ; Cost: 25,705 credits Abilities Concealed Vibrodaggers: The SD-X Stealth Battle Droid has Vibrodaggers completely concealed within its fingers. Extending the Vibrodaggers is a Swift Action . The Droid usually attacks with multiple Vibrodaggers at the same time, dealing extra damage (already included above). Stealth Coating: The SD-X Stealth Battle Droid is sheathed in a black, nonreflective, sensor-resistant coating. When in darkness or shadowy illumination, the Droid gains a +5 bonus to its Stealth checks. When an opponent uses sensors to scan for the Droid, it can make a Stealth check against the opponent's Use Computer check to remain undetected. Threat Scan: As a Full-Round Action , the SD-X Stealth Battle Droid makes a DC 20 Perception check to detect living beings, explosives, or other obvious threats within a 30-meter radius of itself. Success indicates a general description of the threat and its direction and distance from the Droid. SD-X Stealth Battle Droid Protocol Format See also: Protocol Format Medium 4th-Degree Droid Hit Points: 68 Damage Threshold : 24 System Actions Move (1 Swift Action , 2/Turn) The SD-X Stealth Battle Droid moves 6 squares ( Walking ). Blaster Rifle Attack (1 Swift Action , 1/Turn) The SD-X Stealth Battle Droid makes a ranged attack at +9. If successful, the attack deals 3d8+4 points of damage. Circumstantial Stealth Checks (1 Swift Action , 1/Turn) The SD-X Stealth Battle Droid makes a Stealth check. When in darkness or shadowy illumination, the Droid gains a +5 bonus to its Stealth check. When an opponent uses sensors to scan for the Droid, the Droid makes a Stealth check against the opponent's Use Computer check to remain undetected. Concealed Vibrodaggers (2 Swift Actions , 1/Turn) The SD-X Stealth Battle Droid makes a melee attack at +10. If successful, the attack deals 4d4+7 points of damage. Threat Scan (2 Swift Actions , 1/Turn) The SD-X Stealth Battle Droid makes a DC 20 Perception check to detect living beings, explosives, or other obvious threats within a 30-meter radius of itself. Success indicates a general description of the threat and its direction and distance from the Droid. Base Stats"},"cl":9},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"swse":{"speedText":"6 Squares ( Walking ); Hidden Movement","droidSystemText":"Walking Locomotion, Heuristic Processor , 2 Hand Appendages, Darkvision , Improved Sensor Package , Internal Comlink (Encrypted), Locked Access , Vocabulator"}}}
