, Basic Processor , 1 Claw Appendage, Improved Sensor Package , Cloaking Holoprojector","sourcePossessions":"Laser Cannons (As Light Repeating Blaster ), Static Mine (24), Minelayer, Remote Detonator Availability: Military ; Cost: 15,750 credits Abilities [ ] Cloaking Holoprojector: The Techno Union retains the original Droids' traction-field generators, which allow the Spelunkers to walk on walls and ceilings, planting their Mines completely undetected. This grants the Spelunker Probe Droid Total Concealment ."},"cl":6},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"swse":{"speedText":"6 Squares ( Walking ), 3 Squares (Climbing); Hidden Movement","droidSystemText":"Walking Locomotion, Extra Legs , Climbing Claws , Basic Processor , 1 Claw Appendage, Improved Sensor Package , Cloaking Holoprojector"}}}
{"_id":"dba50f4640e22c5c","name":"SD-9_Battle_Droid","type":"droid","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","system":{"degree":"4th-Degree","initiative":15,"senses":"Perception","perception":15,"reflexDefense":30,"flatFooted":27,"fortitudeDefense":39,"willDefense":26,"HP":108,"damageThreshold":44,"speed":6,"baseAttackBonus":null,"grapple":null,"attacks":{"melee":[{"name":"Unarmed","bonus":25,"damage":"1d6+17"}],"ranged":[{"name":"Heavy Repeating Blaster","bonus":15,"damage":"3d10+10, 2-Square Autofire"},{"name":"Heavy Repeating Blaster","bonus":15,"damage":"5d10+10"},{"name":"Plasma Burst Cannon","bonus":20,"damage":"3d12+10, 1-Square Splash"},{"name":"Plasma Burst Cannon","bonus":20,"damage":"3d12+10, 1-Square Splash"}]},"baseStats":{"abilities":{"strength":29,"dexterity":15,"intelligence":10,"wisdom":11,"charisma":8,"constitution":0}},"skills":{"Endurance":13,"Initiative":15,"Perception":15},"type":"droid","description":"","costNumeric":51405,"category":"droid","cost":51405,"droidDegreeKey":"4th-degree","droidRole":"heavy","droidRoleLabel":"Heavy","droidSystemText":"Walking Locomotion, Basic Processor , 2 Tool Mounts, Improved Sensor Package , Internal Comlink , Ion Shield Generator (SR 15 (vs Ion )), Locked Access , Vocabulator","droidSystems":{"processor":{"id":"basic-processor","name":"Basic Processor","source":"published"},"locomotion":[{"id":"walking-locomotion","name":"Walking Locomotion","source":"published"}],"appendages":[{"id":"2-tool-mounts","name":"2 Tool Mounts","source":"published"}],"sensors":[{"id":"improved-sensor-package","name":"Improved Sensor Package","source":"published"}],"integratedSystems":[{"id":"internal-comlink","name":"Internal Comlink","source":"published"},{"id":"ion-shield-generator-sr-15-vs-ion","name":"Ion Shield Generator (SR 15 (vs Ion ))","source":"published"},{"id":"locked-access","name":"Locked Access","source":"published"},{"id":"vocabulator","name":"Vocabulator","source":"published"}],"accessories":[],"weapons":[{"id":"heavy-repeating-blaster","name":"Heavy Repeating Blaster","mode":"ranged","damage":"3d10+10, 2-Square Autofire","attackBonus":15,"source":"published-attack"},{"id":"heavy-repeating-blaster","name":"Heavy Repeating Blaster","mode":"ranged","damage":"5d10+10","attackBonus":15,"source":"published-attack"},{"id":"plasma-burst-cannon","name":"Plasma Burst Cannon","mode":"ranged","damage":"3d12+10, 1-Square Splash","attackBonus":20,"source":"published-attack"},{"id":"plasma-burst-cannon","name":"Plasma Burst Cannon","mode":"ranged","damage":"3d12+10, 1-Square Splash","attackBonus":20,"source":"published-attack"}],"sourceText":"Walking Locomotion, Basic Processor , 2 Tool Mounts, Improved Sensor Package , Internal Comlink , Ion Shield Generator (SR 15 (vs Ion )), Locked Access , Vocabulator","sourcePossessions":"Plasma Burst Cannon (as Blaster Cannon ; +1 die of damage if exceeding Damage Threshold ), Heavy Repeating Blaster , Duranium Battle Armor ( Droid Armor ; +10 Reflex ) Availability: Military ; Cost: 51,405 credits Abilities [ ] Defense Mode: As a Swift Action , an SD-9 Battle Droid enters Defense Mode and designates one person, object, or location to defend. While in Defense Mode, once per encounter, as a Reaction , the Droid can make a single attack against one enemy that attacks the designated subject. Swift Assault Mode: Once per encounter, an SD-9 Battle Droid can make a single attack at a -10 penalty as a Swift Action when also taking two Move Actions in the same turn. SD-9 Battle Droid Protocol Format [ ] See also: Protocol Format Large 4th-Degree Droid Hit Points: 108 Damage Threshold : 44 (DR 4; SR 15 (vs Ion )) System Actions [ ] Move (1 Swift Action , 2/Turn) [ ] The SD-9 Battle Droid moves 6 squares ( Walking ). Defense Mode (1 Swift Action , 1/Encounter) [ ] The SD-9 Battle Droid enters Defense Mode and designates one person, object, or location to defend. While in Defense Mode, the Droid makes a single attack against one enemy that attacks the designated subject. Delay Damage ( Reaction ) [ ] The SD-9 Battle Droid delays the effect of a single attack, ability, or effect used against it until the end of its next turn. Heavy Repeating Blaster Attack (1 Swift Action , 1/Turn) [ ] The SD-9 Battle Droid makes a ranged Autofire attack at +15. If successful, the attack deals 3d10+10 points of damage in a 2x2-Square area. If unsuccessful, the attack deals half damage. Twin Blaster Burst (1 Swift Action , 1/Turn) [ ] The SD-9 Battle Droid makes a ranged attack at +20. If successful, the attack deals 3d12+10 points of damage with a 1-Square Splash . Base Stats [ ]"},"cl":16},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"swse":{"speedText":"6 Squares ( Walking ); Running Attack","droidSystemText":"Walking Locomotion, Basic Processor , 2 Tool Mounts, Improved Sensor Package , Internal Comlink , Ion Shield Generator (SR 15 (vs Ion )), Locked Access , Vocabulator"}}}
